# Your free, permanent ngrok static domain (e.g. oclay-yourname.ngrok-free.app).
# Set this and the tunnel uses a URL that never changes -- paste it into the GPT
# Action once and never copy-paste again. Leave blank to use a temporary tunnel.
OCLAY_NGROK_DOMAIN=
